SubjectBy-election - Medicine Hat–Cardston–Warner
PrecisOrder directing that a WRIT OF ELECTION do issue in order to fill the vacancy in the House of Commons for the electoral district of Medicine Hat–Cardston–Warner, in the Province of Alberta, with polling to take place on October 24, 2016.
